_:N1cb2d7be42044a438d520ba0010ea613 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Journalists with enquiries for the UK Space Agency should contact the DSIT press office:</p>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n  <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:press@dsit.gov.uk\">press@dsit.gov.uk</a></p>\n\n  <p>Phone: 020 7215 3000</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>This phone number and inbox is monitored at all hours.</p>\n\n<p>If you are not a member of the media, please contact <a href=\"mailto:correspondence@dsit.gov.uk\">correspondence@dsit.gov.uk</a>.</p>\n</div>" .
